{
  "texts": [
    "There is a need to effectively learn both modalities in one framework and adapt LLM in the end-to-end training pipeline 37, 38.",
    "Meanwhile, the clinical text usually contains much noise 39, which will mislead the model learning if directly embedded 40.",
    "How to model the patient similarity in multi-modality learning.",
    "Previous multi-modal methods fuse the embeddings of multi-modal data and cannot mine the latent relations between patients 41.",
    "Learning the patient similarity is inspired by the doctor's clinical practice which will refer to the past and related patients' history."
  ]
}